flowchart LR
  H[Host / IMC IPC] --> I[ipc_cmd]
  I --> P[proc_list: context/stream/MCQD table]
  P --> Q[qdma query thread]
  Q --> T[task_list priority queues]
  T --> B[bdma bind thread]
  B --> R[top_reg bind DMA registers]
  R --> HCQD[HCQD active]
  HCQD --> U[CP User cmd_entry]
  U --> FWSTOP[CPE_FW_HCQD_STOPPED]
  FWSTOP --> B
